{"tid":31520,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實上討論區上得咁認真果班人乜事呀？","createTime":"2016-12-09T17:14:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-06T07:16:08.000Z","uid":35400,"like":14,"dislike":88,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dfa279826ffd0bea8c6bca5caebde20f03df445f","tid":31520,"uid":35400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T17:14:09.000Z","msg":"係咪個以為自己讀緊中學要守校規呀<br />\n明明只係一個討論區 <br />\n人地鍾意打乜字又唔得  <br />\n叫下 Ching 又唔得<br />\n個個即刻起哂岡咁  以為一定要跟住自己果套<br />\n咁大個人少少事又投訴又盛<br />\n第時出到黎點樣捱世界呀"},{"pid":"4006512389557aaa3921a7106d3bbb47ef229321","tid":31520,"uid":26213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T17:25:54.000Z","msg":"負評 上一頁"},{"pid":"1d684e6e71b3f6ca06b6b15c3b89907c3a53947c","tid":31520,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T17:33:11.000Z","msg":"有時真係忍唔住笑<br />\n成班矯枉過正 墨守成規<br />\n當然有尐規矩係要守嘅"},{"pid":"2efd19d4afe11b6bd591e718d6bc041deb1bfb30","tid":31520,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T17:36:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有時真係忍唔住笑<br />\n成班矯枉過正 墨守成規<br />\n當然有尐規矩係要守嘅</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n尐你老母"},{"pid":"e713e212b68214997f9ebec3e80ca9d4c51ec35a","tid":31520,"uid":35400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T17:37:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有時真係忍唔住笑<br />\n成班矯枉過正 墨守成規<br />\n當然有尐規矩係要守嘅</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n尐你老母</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n正字都屌<br />\n痴撚左線呀你"},{"pid":"ce31141170f5245e493d0d6c6456309f455d09ab","tid":31520,"uid":5914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T17:39:07.000Z","msg":"正評，上一頁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8f72161d701145ffdd381322e71cdcecf21933d","tid":31520,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T17:45:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有時真係忍唔住笑<br />\n成班矯枉過正 墨守成規<br />\n當然有尐規矩係要守嘅</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n尐你老母</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n正字都屌<br />\n痴撚左線呀你</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n正你老母<br />\n<br />\n尐zit3[1]或zik1，兩個讀音嘅意思都唔一樣。其中：<br />\n讀zit3音嘅意思係少或小，異體字[2]。<br />\n讀zik1音嘅意思係有花紋嘅雌蟬[3]。<br />\n「尐」誤傳為「啲」嘅正字[編輯]<br />\n近年有人將「尐」呢個生僻字，講成係「啲」嘅本字或正字，原因係「尐」解作少，同「啲」（解作一點、一些）有相似嘅地方，更有專欄作家同報章評論員將佢誤傳。「啲」嘅讀音係di1，但「尐」嘅讀音係zit3，尐嘅反切係「子列切」，反切上字取聲母(子-&gt;zi-&gt;z)，下字取韻母(列-&gt;lit-&gt;it)，切出嚟嘅音就係zit，讀音都唔啱，所以無可能係本字或正字。而且意思唔係相同，例如「多啲」（多一點），如果寫成「多尐」就會變成（多少），意思已經唔同咗。"},{"pid":"fa053bcf8aec6c7f280a9e9f9bff1ee55e8b6e13","tid":31520,"uid":11388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T17:48:11.000Z","msg":"牛ching👍🏼"},{"pid":"0d3a0316169f3e415e264c9b2418688cd3d5df06","tid":31520,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T17:52:29.000Z","msg":"有班癡漢話唔識專用術語或唔認得潮文嘅真心膠都有罪 要block<br />\n<br />\n屌<br />\n咁唔撚使有新會員上啦<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">好多冇上開高登嘅真絲/藍絲來咗拉登咖</span>"},{"pid":"cd85e51ae912a93d3f6540075a1bfe184c690607","tid":31520,"uid":50533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T17:53:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bc2ac317c900612cbee9973880f0b436f7485a59","tid":31520,"uid":35400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T17:56:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>負評 上一頁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n不服不辯"},{"pid":"b9efda0134fed2acea93ba730dc583b35671e15d","tid":31520,"uid":35400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T17:56:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>負評 上一頁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n不服來辯</blockquote>"},{"pid":"d440f44298e059a5949925d587e9394ca22c7148","tid":31520,"uid":35400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T17:57:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有班癡漢話唔識專用術語或唔認得潮文嘅真心膠都有罪 要block<br />\n<br />\n屌<br />\n咁唔撚使有新會員上啦<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">好多冇上開高登嘅真絲/藍絲來咗拉登咖</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />